    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We identified patients with coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) in a telemedicine clinic who requested ongoing follow-up 6 weeks after symptom onset. Patients with prolonged symptoms often have not returned to work or usual activity. Respiratory symptoms are most common, and underlying asthma and lung disease occur frequently.</jats:p>",
